'''Explore & More Children's Museum''' was founded in 1994.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.exploreandmore.org/default.aspx |title=Explore & More Children's Museum |publisher=Exploreandmore.org |date= |accessdate=2014-04-19}}</ref> The museum is based in [[East Aurora, New York]]. Currently, a new museum is under construction in downtown [[Buffalo, New York|Buffalo]] in the [[Canalside]] district, slated to open in Spring 2019.<ref>https://www.buffalorising.com/2018/07/construction-watch-explore-and-more-gets-bricked/</ref>

